Together the House Democratic Majority and a White House back on the side of the people will fight to ensure that every family has access to opportunity
We have shattered the glass ceiling with the historic election of Kamala Harris whose presence in the White House is a milestone in our march toward equality for women and women of color.

The American people have chosen hope. President-elect Joe Biden and Vice President-elect Kamala Harris are ready to heal our nation tear down the walls of division and rebuild trust in our democracy and each other. https://t.co/l9C0du2H9g
With your partnership and this commitment to equality as our guiding star we will ensure every family can succeed and that our nation’s future is bright. Thank you again for your confidence.

From health care access to racial injustice to climate change to voting rights the threats facing our planet and democracy are great. We need bold solutions and urgent action to allow us to live up to our nation’s promise of liberty and justice for all.

Delivering a national strategy to contain the virus and stabilize our families and our businesses remain my number one priority.   This moment in our history demands not just recovery but rebirth. We must finally confront the challenges that have long plagued America.

There is much work to be done. The COVID-19 pandemic has shaken our community and our economy to their core. Americans are sick and suffering and have waited too long for relief and real science-based solutions to this crippling public health crisis.
